Reviewed-by: Vasanthakumar Thiagarajan <vasanthakumar.thiagarajan@oss.qualcomm.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250523-ath12k-unicast-key-first-v1-2-f53c3880e6d8@quicinc.com
